@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dtnbrg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs((0.17 + v1))
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v1 + 0.86)) - ((v1 + 0.94 / v2 + 0.54) * 0.77))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.cos((tmp + 0.79 + v0 + 0.40)))
    tmp = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.20 / tmp + 0.78)) - wp.exp(wp.abs(v2 + 0.26)))
    data[tid] = v0
